{"title":"满江红  哥伦比亚航天飞机遇难","authors":["沈鹏"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":2,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"满江红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥伦比亚航天飞机遇难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沈鹏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有际无边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"混茫里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七星隐列。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"念昨日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志冲霄汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑言相别。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船近家园遭不测，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身熔大化何仓卒！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电波传，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火里凤凰生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诚英烈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真勇士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追日月。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河岳近，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思超越。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屈原昂首问，（注一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸甘焦渴。（注二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑洞深通相对论，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光年邈远时空迭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鉴前车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后继者争雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无穷绝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注一：屈原《天问》。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注二：夸父追日，传说见《山海经》。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":15,"page_end":15}